    skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/org/agent-contact-method> ;
    rdfs:label "Phone"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "Preferred contact method is phone."@en .

# Generic Concept for TroubleTicketCharacteristic
<https://w3id.org/noria/data/concept/critical-impact-characteristic>
    a skos:Concept ;
    rdfs:label "Critical Impact Characteristic"@en ;
